As the topic suggests, this post was typed by Jen. Hotmail isn't
letting her log in, so I am to send this for her. The following is her
writing:

-----------------------------------------

+++Element Galactors Cyndro+++

Element jumped into the air, turned, and avoided a lot of missiles.
Many shots riddled his armor but did barely any damage. He picked out
the largest robot on the battle field, which was Menasor, and ran at
him while he fired two missiles at the gestalt.


The Galactor jets both detected Megatron cowardly escaping into
Astroblast, and headed for the Decepticon. They came to position
behind him and each launched two missiles at Astroblast. The
Vycir/Slasys jet was still cloaked.


Missile after missile hit the Maximal City, and for the first time,
Cyndro felt the shields weaken by a precentage point. But the
Decepticon achievement was short lived, because seconds later the
Cybertronian Fire's old shield generators were online, and Maximal
City's shield flared brighter than it was before and extended a bit.
Cyndro could see that a lot of bots were coming in for CR treatment,
so he had lights turn on on the ground of the hallways to lead to the
CR room.
